----------------------------
1. System Requirement

	*Operation system: Ubuntu 14.04
	*50 GB of available hard-disk space needed.

----------------------------
2.Install essential library for host

	$source build/envsetup.sh
	$autoenvsetup

-----------------------------
3.Compile image

	$lunch
	# select the specifies number
	$make

Wait the make finish,you will get the following files:

	out/product/BASEBOARD/image/u-boot-with-spl.bin
	out/product/BASEBOARD/image/uImage
	out/product/BASEBOARD/image/system.*

NOTE: BASEBOARD is your board name.

